    "title": "A good friend sent me this earlier today, and I'm absolutely blown away. Joyeeta...",
    "description": "A good friend sent me this earlier today, and I'm absolutely blown away. Joyeeta Datta, a secondary school student from Narsingdi, Bangladesh, performed 'I See Red' (by Everybody Loves an Outlaw) incredibly well. She's only 15, but her mature control over such a difficult track truly deserves respect. Well done to 'Yamaha Next Gen Fusion' for introducing us to Joyeeta. All the best to this young lady. Video courtesy Yamaha Music Bangladesh - ACI Motors Ltd.",
